    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I found the following summary very useful: <a href=\"http://www.techrepublic.com/article/configure-vi-for-java-application-development/5054618\">http://www.techrepublic.com/article/configure-vi-for-java-application-development/5054618</a>. The description of :make was for ant not maven, but otherwise a nice summary. </p>\n"
